{"tid":2132780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★中港貨車司機：檢測檢到流鼻血仍遭歧視　禁踏足小區如過街老鼠","createTime":"2020-07-30T14:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T08:45:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6e309085876c40de7cb54da35abd6532fc014a65","tid":2132780,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:46:28.000Z","msg":"從事跨境貨車司機逾30年的李先生形容，是次疫情令中港司機面臨回歸以來「最麻煩」時刻，每個口岸做法不一，「過一次關就做一次檢測，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">撩到鼻都流血</span></strong>」；而首現中港貨車司機確診個案後，內地再次收緊防疫措施，一度要求司機在8小時內往返，現時雖未有嚴格執行，但內地廣東省多個「小區」已紛紛禁止中港司機踏足該區，逾千名司機有家歸不得，他批評，港府放寬船員及機組人員入境，釀成第三波大爆發，致中港司機被視為「帶病毒」，情況猶如「過街老鼠」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/504957/%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E8%B2%A8%E8%BB%8A%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F-%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E6%AA%A2%E5%88%B0%E6%B5%81%E9%BC%BB%E8%A1%80%E4%BB%8D%E9%81%AD%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96-%E7%A6%81%E8%B8%8F%E8%B6%B3%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%80%E5%A6%82%E9%81%8E%E8%A1%97%E8%80%81%E9%BC%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F504957%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%25B5%2581%25E9%25BC%25BB%25E8%25A1%2580%25E4%25BB%258D%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25AD%25A7%25E8%25A6%2596-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%25B8%258F%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%25A6%2582%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%25A1%2597%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%25BC%25A0&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSrtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=8a2c56c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/504957/%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E8%B2%A8%E8%BB%8A%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F-%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E6%AA%A2%E5%88%B0%E6%B5%81%E9%BC%BB%E8%A1%80%E4%BB%8D%E9%81%AD%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96-%E7%A6%81%E8%B8%8F%E8%B6%B3%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%80%E5%A6%82%E9%81%8E%E8%A1%97%E8%80%81%E9%BC%A0</a>"},{"pid":"1d46de74ef7901ef27d2b051636bf50fc5621f6b","tid":2